HEADWORD: Pooling
<hw>Pool"ing</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Law)</fld> <def>The act of
uniting, or an agreement to unite, an aggregation of properties
belonging to different persons, with a view to common liabilities or
profits.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Poon</ent>⟦br⟧
